high_descs: Go across the room towards the door, hang a right, go forward, hang a left and go to the wall, turn to the left to face the table.
Pick up the butter knife that is between the lettuce and the bowl on the table.
Cut the tomato that is on the table into slices.
Turn to the left and go to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, turn left to face the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn around, go to the right to the counter, turn to the right, hang a left and go to the microwave on the other side of the room.
Put the tomato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the tomato when it is done cooking.
Turn around, go to the table, hang a right and go to the fridge.
Put the tomato inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked tomato into the fridge.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the door and turn right, then go past the table and turn left, go behind the chair and turn left again so that you are facing the table.
Pick up the knife between the head of lettuce and the bowl, on the table,
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn to the refrigerator behind you.
Place the knife on the shelf above the drawers, in the refrigerator.
Turn back around, towards the table where the tomato is.
Pick up one of the slices of tomato on the table.
Turn to your left and go across the kitchen to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the tomato slice from the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk back towards the table and turn right, towards the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice on the shelf above the drawers, in the refrigerator, to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a warm tomato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go forward and go to the right side of the gray round table.
Pick up the gray knife between the lettuce and the gray bowl.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn left and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the gray knife in the freezer
Turn left to go back to the table with the sliced tomato.
Pick up one end slice of the tomato from the table.
Turn left and go to the microwave across the kitchen.
Remove the tomato slice after heating it in the microwave next to the apples.
Turn around and go back to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice in the freezer on the right of the gray knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato slice in the freezer
